{"tid":2125517,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣州街頭抗議被刑拘逾月  維權者反國安惡法 手腳遭扣連變「人球」","createTime":"2020-07-26T08:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T09:10:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e70b49a9146fd9d8826f6b67f4a2ee08584aea66","tid":2125517,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/RW23RPXMW7V77CLBPFW6NYZOXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FRW23RPXMW7V77CLBPFW6NYZOXQ%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLg3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=24c0fdc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FRW23RPXMW7V77CLBPFW6NYZOXQ%2F&h=c1b8b33f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/RW23RPXMW7V77CLBPFW6NYZOXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n廣州街頭抗議被刑拘逾月 <br />\n維權者反國安惡法 手腳遭扣連變「人球」<br />\n<br />\n內地女維權人士張五洲上月廣州街頭舉牌展示「勿忘六四、撤回惡法」標語，反對全國人大通過訂立港版國安法及紀念六四31周年，張遭刑拘個多月後，其家屬對本報表示她在看守所遭受酷刑，手腳多日來被十分重的鐵鐐扣在一起，整個人猶如人球，張五洲又說同倉毆打她，讓她「生不如死」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oFJoq_3ROa2feysZNHcLpYXOzNs=/476x564/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZZWWWNA3GQQL5PEQXXMJPM6SPY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoFJoq_3ROa2feysZNHcLpYXOzNs%3D%2F476x564%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZZWWWNA3GQQL5PEQXXMJPM6SPY.gif&h=c7fd697c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n維權人士張五洲上月六四在街頭舉「撤回惡法」標語，翌日被拘留。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n張五洲妹妹張唯楚前日接受本報電話訪問，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據張唯楚請來的律師引述，張五洲在會面時，見到律師即大哭，指自己在看守所中遭受酷刑，雙腳一直要戴着一個十分重的腳鐐，手上的手銬則扣在腳鐐上，讓她整個人一直屈曲，就像一個「人球」一樣，這樣的情況持續了整整六天。在這段時間，又有同倉的人毆打她，張五洲對律師哭訴，在看守所裏面「生不如死」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8v6Cj_1rDEfSUVaGIaCCQ2z75hE=/680x441/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WGS6Y4WJWG2W543XCXFLD2CZH4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8v6Cj_1rDEfSUVaGIaCCQ2z75hE%3D%2F680x441%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWGS6Y4WJWG2W543XCXFLD2CZH4.gif&h=16219ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張五洲（右二）過往與其他維權者到法院外爭取權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拒簽空白通知書<br />\n<br />\n張唯楚說，之前有法援律師表示見到張五洲，說她在看守所中情緒穩定，狀態良好，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。對方才說張五洲於上月20日已被批捕，而且增加了防礙公務罪名，張唯楚才察覺到這法援律師有問題。對方也指，妨礙公務罪是源於派出所強迫張五洲簽一份空白的刑拘通知書，張五洲不肯，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張五洲的弟弟張六毛2015年也因維權被控以「尋釁滋事罪」，遭拘留廣州第三看守所，但在兩個月後卻在看守所暴斃。當時新華社、央視等官媒罕有地以大篇幅報道維權事件，指張六毛等人要通過武裝暴動改變現有體制。"},{"pid":"2799b5701ab942bc31cc41882d156189cfe76d2b","tid":2125517,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"六世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07713f460f0c0c1f52572faa29be73dbf140f5e8","tid":2125517,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b87bdcc42578d8aed58f481e5d279c194d4f9b3","tid":2125517,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}